{id:"item-amulet-of-the-planes",name:"Amulet of the Planes",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Amulet of the Planes"},{id:"Image",url:"https://www.dnd5eapi.co/api/images/magic-items/amulet-of-the-planes.png"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Category",content:"Wondrous Items"},{title:"Rarity",content:"Very Rare"}]},{id:"MultiText",content:["Wondrous item, very rare (requires attunement)","While wearing this amulet, you can use an action to name a location that you are familiar with on another plane of existence. Then make a DC 15 Intelligence check. On a successful check, you cast the plane shift spell. On a failure, you and each creature and object within 15 feet of you travel to a random destination. Roll a d100. On a 1-60, you travel to a random location on the plane you named. On a 61-100, you travel to a randomly determined plane of existence."]}]}